 好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a4d04a379b8d62960b766c4ab775a34df6b6bd","tid":249964,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:26:49.000Z","msg":"殺呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5663a437bfab35e2c408fa1d3227e4d0b91d4d3d","tid":249964,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:27:00.000Z","msg":"打波要有戰術 殺甲由都一定要有戰術"},{"pid":"cb1b2a77d09fbc4ec817b025ccf7b0323e1ed29b","tid":249964,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"我屋企個廚房又係多撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成撚日半日都會走出黎,核突到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我又唔敢搞佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e646c617c9ff7f1db67ee708aa4aba333b8a3c","tid":249964,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企個廚房又係多撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成撚日半夜都會走出黎,核突到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我又唔敢搞佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8a58a2cf236ff34f2971243f3880992b95b9c5e7","tid":249964,"uid":81751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"屌 寫慎入嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced82578da